# Homelab Firewall Rules (Current State)

## Overview
This document defines the current firewall rules implemented in OPNsense.  
Rules are organized by VLAN and follow a top-down evaluation model (first match wins).

---

## Global Notes

- All rules are evaluated **top → bottom**
- Implicit **deny all** at the end of each interface
- Aliases are used for readability and scalability
- Some rules are intentionally permissive and will be hardened later

---

## MGMT VLAN (192.168.99.0/24)

**Purpose:** Administrative control plane

| Priority | Action | Source     | Destination | Port | Description |
|----------|--------|-----------|------------|------|------------|
| 1 | PASS | MGMT_NET | ANY | ANY | Full admin access (temporary) |
| 2 | PASS | MGMT_NET | WAN | ANY | Internet access for admin |

---

## TEST VLAN (192.168.20.0/24)

**Purpose:** Controlled testing environment

| Priority | Action | Source     | Destination      | Port            | Description |
|----------|--------|-----------|-----------------|-----------------|------------|
| 1 | PASS | TEST_NET | SPLUNK_SERVER | SPLUNK_PORT (9997) | Log forwarding |
| 2 | PASS | TEST_NET | AD_SERVER     | AD_PORTS        | Domain services |
| 3 | PASS | TEST_NET | WAN           | ANY             | Internet access |
| - | DENY | TEST_NET | ANY           | ANY             | Implicit deny |

---

## HOME VLAN (192.168.30.0/24)

**Purpose:** Personal / family devices

| Priority | Action | Source     | Destination | Port | Description |
|----------|--------|-----------|------------|------|------------|
| 1 | BLOCK | HOME_NET | SERVERS_NET | ANY | Prevent access to servers |
| 2 | BLOCK | HOME_NET | MGMT_NET | ANY | Prevent access to admin network |
| 3 | BLOCK | HOME_NET | TEST_NET | ANY | Prevent access to test environment |
| 4 | PASS | HOME_NET | WAN | ANY | Internet access |
| - | DENY | HOME_NET | ANY | ANY | Implicit deny |

---

## IOT VLAN (192.168.40.0/24)

**Purpose:** Untrusted / smart devices

| Priority | Action | Source   | Destination | Port | Description |
|----------|--------|---------|------------|------|------------|
| 1 | BLOCK | IOT_NET | SERVERS_NET | ANY | Prevent access to servers |
| 2 | BLOCK | IOT_NET | MGMT_NET | ANY | Prevent access to admin network |
| 3 | PASS | IOT_NET | WAN | ANY | Internet access |
| - | DENY | IOT_NET | ANY | ANY | Implicit deny |

---

## SERVERS VLAN (192.168.60.0/24)

**Purpose:** Core infrastructure

| Priority | Action | Source        | Destination | Port | Description |
|----------|--------|--------------|------------|------|------------|
| 1 | PASS | MGMT_NET    | SERVERS_NET | ANY | Administrative access |
| 2 | PASS | SERVERS_NET | WAN         | ANY | Outbound connectivity (temporary) |
| 3 | BLOCK | SERVERS_NET | TEST_NET    | ANY | Prevent access to test VLAN |
| - | DENY | SERVERS_NET | ANY         | ANY | Implicit deny |

---

## SANDBOX VLAN (192.168.50.0/24)

**Purpose:** Isolated malware testing environment

| Priority | Action | Source       | Destination | Port | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|------------|------|------------|
| 1 | PASS | MGMT_NET    | SANDBOX_NET | ANY | Admin access to sandbox |
| 2 | BLOCK | SANDBOX_NET | SERVERS_NET | ANY | Prevent lateral movement |
| - | DENY | SANDBOX_NET | ANY         | ANY | Full isolation (no internet) |

